 \vec{r}(t)=\left(e^{\omega t}(\cos(\omega t)+\sin(\omega t)),2\omega e^{\omega t} \cos(\omega t)\right) 
\frac{x}{y}
\tan
\quad\displaystyle R(x,y) = \sqrt{\left(\frac{y}{2\omega}\right)^2 + \left(x - \frac{y}{2\omega}\right)^2}
R(x,y) - \frac{y}{2\omega}\cos\log R(x,y)  - \left(x - \frac{y}{2\omega}\right)\sin\log R(x,y) = 0
\frac{y}{2\omega}\sin\log R(x,y) - \left(x - \frac{y}{2\omega}\right)\cos\log R(x,y) = 0
